WEBVTT

00:06:28.886 --> 00:06:30.115
(Laughter)

00:06:31.037 --> 00:06:36.133
But genetically, we are all
99.9 percent the same.

00:06:36.157 --> 00:06:41.359
There's more genetic diversity
within what we call racial groups

00:06:41.383 --> 00:06:44.012
than there is between racial groups.

00:06:44.036 --> 00:06:47.983
There's no gene for whiteness
or blackness or Asian-ness

00:06:48.007 --> 00:06:49.440
or what have you.

00:06:50.411 --> 00:06:52.406
So how did this happen?

00:06:52.430 --> 00:06:54.383
How did we get this thing?

00:06:54.407 --> 00:06:56.497
How did racism start?

00:06:57.797 --> 00:07:01.303
I think if you had asked me
to speculate on that,